      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-kjv2006/PSA010.htm",
      "text": "The wicked, through the pride of his countenance, will not seek [after God:] God [is] not in all his thoughts.",
      "versionTitle": "King James Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 10:4",
      "source_id": "asv",
      "source_url": "https://ebible.org/eng-asv/PSA010.htm",
      "text": "The wicked, in the pride of his countenance, [saith], He will not require [it]. All his thoughts are, There is no God.",
      "versionTitle": "American Standard Version"
    },
    {
      "language": "en",
      "ref": "Psalm 10:4",
